{"tid":1513572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非愚見","createTime":"2019-08-28T11:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T11:31:01.000Z","uid":281298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7346a7227b2c862f6109e88cca5c29789f737185","tid":1513572,"uid":281298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:29:47.000Z","msg":"最近香港吹完和風，跟住升級暴力鎮壓，貿易戰又加美國關稅，跟住打電話去求和，可見習總已非定於一尊，各派系佢都控制唔住，胡溫被稱為弱主，九龍治水，都不致於咁，可見中共內部鬥爭幾咁激烈，情況越來越似蘇聯解體前。但在分崩離析前我地會面對一段很黑暗的日子，我認為應該停止所有勇武抗爭，避免損失，大家持續和理非抗爭的同時保護好自己，遊行要戴口罩、帽，等待更好的時機出現"},{"pid":"82aea3c979f48581b5050a8231ac6f916806de00","tid":1513572,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:30:17.000Z","msg":"[置頂-連登改變世界]929全球集會抗赤納粹，召喚攬炒巴，G20巴，動畫巴，各文宣巴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n#Chinazi<br />\n#ProtectOurCountry<br />\n#StandwithHongKong<br />\n#NomadeinChina"},{"pid":"e5d7274e9fb736650eddecad4fea1090d03d0083","tid":1513572,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5HjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=7e49a02d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5HjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=1749f581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen